streamripper: Streamripper (Rip SHOUTcast Radio Streams to MP3 Files)
streamripper:
streamripper: Streamripper records SHOUTcast and Icecast compatible streams.
streamripper: It uses meta data within a SHOUTcast stream to determine the
streamripper: beginning and end of each song, and stores the songs on your
streamripper: hard disk as individual mp3 files. In addition, Streamripper
streamripper: includes a relay server for listening to the station while
streamripper: you are recording.
streamripper:
streamripper: Homepage: http://streamripper.sourceforge.net/
